org.nasdanika.html.model.app

Interface NavigationBar

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Adaptable, BootstrapElement, EObject, HtmlElement, Marked, ModelElement, Notifier, PagePart
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NavigationBarImpl

    public interface NavigationBar
extends PagePart
    A representation of the model object 'Navigation Bar'. Navigation bar has a brand and navigation items.

    The following features are supported:

    • Brand
    • Dark
    • Expand
    • Background
    See Also:
    AppPackage.getNavigationBar()
